title: AS Kaloum Star
text:
Association Sportive Kaloum , also known as A.S.K, is a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Conakry">Conakry</a>, <a href="Guinea">Guinea</a>. In the 1960s A.S.K was known as Conakry I, and won three titles under that name.
Due to the problems in sponsoring in 2008, the club was relegated to Ligue 2.
